@{selected|wtype}&{template:traits} @{selected|charname_output} {{name=Spell Slot Recovery}} {{source=Class: Sorcerer (DD)}} {{description=Recovering Spell Slots
As a bonus action on your turn, you can transform unexpended sorcery points into one or more spell slots. The Restoring Spell Slots table shows the cost of creating a spell slot of a given level. You can create spell slots no higher in level than 5th.

Recovering Spell Slots
1st = 2 SP
2nd = 3 SP
3rd = 5 SP
4th = 6 SP
5th = 7 SP}}
